response.overview: From the makers of "Actuality of Thought" and "Automatic Magnetic 1.0," comes a snapshot of underground Rock in 2002, filmed live from Michigan Fest. Bands include Rye Coalition, Crooked Fingers, Aloha, Arab on Radar, The Arrivals, Berwer, Casket Lottery, Coalesce, Constantines, Creation is Crucifixion, Crush Kill Destroy, Death Cab for Cutie, Dillinger 4, Dismemberment Plan, End It, Few and Far Between, Haymarket Riot, Hey Mercedes, Honor System, Hot Snakes, Inside Five Minutes, Isis, Keleton DMD, Leaving Rouge, Milemarker, Owls, Oxes, Planes Mistaken for Stars, lots more.
response.title: MichiganFest 2002 Documented
